doctype html5
html
  head
    title Twidd.ly
    link(rel="stylesheet", type="text/css", href="style.css")
  body
    main
      section#title
        .header
          img(src="images/twiddlyWatermarkBlue.png")
        .story
          .caption
            h2 Transcend Boredom
            p Twiddly brings the best of the web, right to your lockscreen
          img(src="images/lockFencePhone.png", alt="")
          .mobile-caption
            h2 Transcend Boredom
            p Twiddly brings the best of the web, right to your lockscreen
      section#curated
        .header
          img(src="images/twiddlyWatermark.png")
        .story
          img(src="images/themeChooser.png", alt="")
          .caption
            h2 Stories that inspire you
            p Choose from curated themes to get handpicked stories you'd enjoy.
          .mobile-caption
            h2 Stories that inspire you
            p Choose from curated themes to get handpicked stories you'd enjoy.
      section#lockscreen
        .header
          img(src="images/twiddlyWatermark.png")
        .story
          .caption
            h2 Dive right in
            p Read articles, watch videos and browse stories without unlocking your phone.
      section#snacky
        .header
          img(src="images/twiddlyWatermarkBlue.png")
        .story
          img(src="images/barkContentPhone.png", alt="")
          .caption
            h2 Stories that pack a punch
            p Snack away on stories that are no longer than 5 minutes!
      section#founders
        .header
          img(src="images/twiddlyWatermark.png")
        .section-title
          h2 The Team
        .story
          .container
            img(src="images/ranjan.jpg", alt="")
            .caption
              | <h3>Ranjan Jagannathan</h3> is a Stanford Ignite alum. He led customer development, product experiments and analytics for a 500 Startups company, Mygola. Before that, he was an innovation program manager with Yahoo! India where he designed and ran large scale innovation programs.
          .container
            img(src="images/sanjay.jpg", alt="")
            .caption
              | <h3>Sanjay Guruprasad </h3> is an engineering grad from IIT Madras. He worked at an iBank but quit his job after a year to get back to coding. He developed an alerts system for the iOT startup MagnetWorks. He also headed 'Enerji' at Softrade - a product that helps factories move to cleaner fuels.
      section#signup-form
        .header
          img(src="images/twiddlyWatermarkBlue.png")
        .section-title
          h1 Sign Up!
        form(id="signup", method="POST", action="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1dv0Ow2ik-zTlLn3y6qdMje04sjUypou5P16F1r4pb7I/formResponse")
          .info
            p Twiddly is coming to your lockscreen soon!
            p.hug Get early access by signing up for the beta below.
          select(name="entry.1200618361", id="entry_1200618361", placeholder="Choose Phone", required)
            option(default) Which phone do you own?
            option iPhone
            option Windows
            option Other
            option Android
          input(name="entry.1422492071", id="entry_1422492071", placeholder="Email address", required)
          button(type="submit", name="submit", value="Submit") Sign up for a sneak peak!

  footer


